<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hesap360 | Karanlık Finansal Analiz Gücü</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root { 
            --bg: #020617; 
            --surface: #0f172a; 
            --primary: #3b82f6; 
            --primary-glow: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
            --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08); 
            --text-dim: #94a3b8; 
        }

        body { 
            background: var(--bg); font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; color: #fff; margin: 0; 
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 50% -20%, var(--primary-glow) 0%, transparent 50%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }

        /* Canlı Piyasa Bandı - Karanlık Versiyon */
        .ticker { 
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 12px 0; font-size: 0.85rem; 
        }
        .ticker b { color: var(--primary); margin-left: 5px; }
        .status-dot { color: #10b981; margin-left: 5px; font-size: 0.7rem; }

        nav { padding: 25px 0; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        .logo { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; }
        .logo span { color: var(--primary); }

        .hero { text-align: center; padding: 60px 0 40px; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.2; }
        .hero h1 span { color: var(--primary); }

        /* Sekmeler - Neon Stil */
        .tabs { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .tab-btn {
            background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-dim);
            padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 50px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .tab-btn.active { background: var(--primary); color: #fff; border-color: var(--primary); box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--primary-glow); }

        /* Pro Grid Layout */
        .main-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
            gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .tool-card {
            background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 20px; padding: 30px 15px; text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
        }

        .tool-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px); border-color: var(--primary);
            background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.05); box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        .tool-card i { font-size: 2rem; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 18px; }
        .tool-card span { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.2px; }

        /* Fırsat Kartları */
        .promo-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }
        .promo {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--surface) 0%, #1e293b 100%);
            border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 24px; padding: 30px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .promo:hover { border-color: var(--primary); }
        .promo-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; background: var(--primary-glow); width: 70px; height: 70px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border-radius: 18px; }

        @media (max-width: 1024px) { .main-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); } }
        @media (max-width: 600px) { .main-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } .promo-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="ticker">
    <div class="container">
        <span>USD<b>32.45</b></span> &nbsp; <span>EUR<b>35.12</b></span> &nbsp; <span>XAU<b>2450</b></span>
        <span style="float:right;"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle status-dot"></i> Piyasalar Açık</span>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <nav>
        <a href="/" class="logo">HESAP<span>360</span></a>
        <div style="color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600;">DARK MODE V2.0</div>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero">
        <h1>Finansal İhtiyaçların İçin<br><span>Akıllı Çözümler</span></h1>
    </header>

    <div class="tabs">
        <button class="tab-btn active">Krediler</button>
        <button class="tab-btn">Mevduat / Yatırım</button>
    </div>

    <div class="main-grid">
        <a href="/kredi" class="tool-card"><i class="fa-solid fa-money-bill-transfer"></i><span>İhtiyaç Kredisi</span></a>
        <a href="/kredi-karti" class="tool-card"><i class="fa-solid fa-credit-card"></i><span>Kredi Kartı</span></a>
        <a href="/mevduat" class="tool-card"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-trend-up"></i><span>Mevduat</span></a>
        <a href="/kredi" class="tool-card"><i class="fa-solid fa-building-user"></i><span>Konut Kredisi</span></a>
        <a href="/kredi" class="tool-card"><i class="fa-solid fa-car-side"></i><span>Taşıt Kredisi</span></a>
        <a href="/kredi-limit" class="tool-card"><i class="fa-solid fa-sliders"></i><span>Limit Analizi</span></a>
    </div>

    <div class="promo-grid">
        <div class="promo">
            <div class="promo-icon">💰</div>
            <div>
                <h3 style="margin:0">Fırsat Kredisi</h3>
                <p style="margin:5px 0; color:var(--text-dim); font-size:0.9rem;">Yeni müşterilere özel %0 faiz avantajı.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="promo">
            <div class="promo-icon">📈</div>
            <div>
                <h3 style="margin:0">Yüksek Getiri</h3>
                <p style="margin:5px 0; color:var(--text-dim); font-size:0.9rem;">%52'ye varan mevduat oranlarını yakala.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer style="margin-top:80px; padding:50px 0; text-align:center; color:var(--text-dim); border-top: 1px solid var(--border);">
        <p>© 2026 Hesap360 | Güçlü, Hızlı ve Karanlık.</p>
    </footer>
</div>

</body>
</html>
